#~ msgid ""
#~ "The text boxes in the grass area are the names of the players in this "
#~ "game. To change the name of the players, change the text in the text "
#~ "boxes. To change the ball color of the players' balls, click the middle "
#~ "button that has a color rectangle, and a dialog will open where you can "
#~ "select the new ball color. The rectangle on the button is the current "
#~ "player's ball color."
